spirit:component.spirit:name: gtp

spirit:enumeration.spirit:text: Include Shared Logic in example design

spirit:component.spirit:description: Use the 7 Series FPGAs Transceivers Wizard to configure one or more Virtex-7/Kintex-7/Artix-7/Zynq FPGA transceivers. Start from scratch, or use an industry standard template. The Wizard generates a custom wrapper for the tranceivers you've selected. In addition, it produces an example design, testbench, and scripts to observe the transceivers operating under simulation and in hardware.
